title: Grateful Dead Live at Shrine Auditorium on 1978-01-11
description:
Set 1

Minglewood Blues, Dire Wolf, Looks Like Rain, They Love Each Other, Big River-> El Paso, Brown Eyed Women, Let It Grow

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Sunrise, Terrapin Station-> Playin' In The Band-> Saint Stephen-> Not Fade Away-> Playin' In The Band, E: Passenger

reviews.review_text:
Noise Reduced Version Such a killer set, one of the best terrapins, heady let it grow jammed out to perfection, perfect drums>st stephen and a bunch more. 
Only thing that killed this show for me was the amount of tape hiss, so I did a little tweaking and managed to get things sounding clearer without compromising the quality. Link is available here: https://mega.nz/folder/BpgSTAYC#2zsXwdD5WggTlKtBSFlibw

Also up on youtube here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3grYGFIL9bk

thanks mister miller!!
